      "span_text": "Cultures of primary HE cells were prepared from the LSH inbred hamster strain (Charles River, Lakeview, Wilmington, Mass., U.S.A.) and were grown in Eagle's minimal essential medium (MEM; Microbiological Associates, Walkersville, Md., U.S.A.) as described previously [CITATION_1] ."
